       ** Community Conversations: Solutions to the Global Crisis **

The What Now show is building a library of conversations with accomplished thinkers, writers, artists, farmers and scientists addressing our global crisis.

This podcast is an archive of the What Now radio show of KOWS Radio 107.3 FM in Occidental, California. http://kows107-3.org

Since 2009, the host Ken Rose has created a valuable library of 400 hour-long conversations with accomplished thinkers, writers, artists, farmers and scientists addressing our global crisis. He continues to interview three guests per week on his local radio program. 
